<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>{{ title }}</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ meta_description }}">
<link rel="canonical" href="{{ canonical }}">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0b5d4a">

<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/img/favicon.svg">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/img/favicon-32.png">
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/img/apple-touch-icon.png">

<meta property="og:title" content="{{ og_title }}">
<meta property="og:description" content="{{ meta_description }}">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta property="og:url" content="{{ canonical }}">

<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
{% block head_extra %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
<a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to content</a>
{% block header %}{% endblock %}
<main id="main" class="wrap">
{% block content %}{% endblock %}
</main>
<footer>
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Was this helpful?</h2>
    <p>This is a free, independent project. If it helped protect your car, a small donation keeps it going — and please share it with anyone who drives.</p>
    <div class="footer-actions">
      <a class="btn" href="https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=LRE8FY2BEMXUE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">❤ Donate via PayPal</a>
      <a class="btn outline" href="/#contribute">Add or fix a car</a>
    </div>
    <p class="footer-fine">
      Instructions are gathered from owner's manuals and car owner communities. Some are marked unverified — always check your own manual.<br>
      <a href="https://github.com/willsheppard/prevent-keyless-car-theft" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open source</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
